<plot>A documentary interview with the Austrian composer Ernst Krenek on the eve of his ninetieth birthday, precedes the performances with the Gustav Mahler Youth Orchestra of two of his works, "Il Transparente" conducted by Vaclav Neumann and "Instant Remembered" conducted by Marc Albrecht with soprano Penelope Walmsley-Clark, the solist.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?414942</url></doc>
